title: Jenkins and Jonez - 2022 Playoff Preview
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - 2022 Playoff Preview
description:
The minute the regular season ends the guys dive into the playoffs and break down every series, what they’re most excited about, and give predictions for who will make it out of each conference. Then they have a Music Discussion about regionality and why they love the new Vince Staples album.
